- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper compares the proposed method with other well-known texture descriptors in the literature. 
- cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) is another possible category as the paper uses the Schroedinger equation from Quantum Mechanics to evolve the probability distribution of the wave function. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is unlikely as the paper does not deal with sound or audio processing.
